Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.26,0:02:52.61,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(370,650)\blur5\pos(507.6,1053.067)}{\1cBCE347}溫{\1cFFFFFF}暖的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.41,0:01:25.61,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}眩しい光が土を照らす
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.81,0:01:31.36,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}そう　そのたねは十分に芽を伸ばせる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.97,0:01:42.12,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}冷たい雨にも　強い風にも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.26,0:01:46.53,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}何者でも揺るがない魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.69,0:01:50.91,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}僕らの背を押すわけはなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.07,0:01:54.63,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}そう　くじけそうになった日もあっただろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.69,0:01:58.42,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}不思議な力あふれ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.76,0:02:05.15,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}愛の指す方へ　駆け出す少年のよう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.84,0:02:09.97,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}長い冬越え　僕ら包む
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.25,0:02:14.34,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}春の息吹　福音になるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.64,0:02:18.74,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}僕は君を探し求めて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.06,0:02:23.19,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}この日をずっと待ち続けた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.41,0:02:27.54,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}信じることの強さをそれない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.78,0:02:31.95,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}それはいつかの孤独を癒すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.95,0:02:38.00,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}あぁ　もしも君が星に帰れと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.21,0:02:43.03,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}新しいたねをまこう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.41,0:01:25.61,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}耀眼的光芒照亮大地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.81,0:01:31.36,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}含苞之種由此茁壯成長
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.97,0:01:42.12,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}無論是冰冷的雨水  還是強勁的烈風
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.26,0:01:46.53,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}這是誰都無法動搖的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.69,0:01:50.91,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}助我們一臂之力的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.07,0:01:54.63,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}曾經也有灰心喪氣的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.69,0:01:58.42,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}不可思議的力量滿溢而出
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.76,0:02:05.15,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}朝著愛的方向奔跑吧  少年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.84,0:02:09.97,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}跨越長冬  將我們包圍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.25,0:02:14.34,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}春天的氣息  成為福音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.64,0:02:18.74,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}我追尋著你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.06,0:02:23.19,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}一直等待今天的到來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.41,0:02:27.54,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}堅信著信任這一強大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.78,0:02:31.95,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}不久它便會治癒你的孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.95,0:02:38.00,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}如果你將回歸繁星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.21,0:02:43.03,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}去播撒新的種子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.26,0:00:18.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開了這麽久了 離目的地還有多遠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.89,0:00:23.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照莫拉說的 過了前面的山嶺那附近就是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.43,0:00:25.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不能開快點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.69,0:00:28.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引擎的情況不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.02,0:00:29.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這已經是最快了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.52,0:00:30.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.77,0:00:35.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要問為何 因為這是集結了瓦洛夫家技術結晶的最高傑作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.11,0:00:35.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.86,0:00:37.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還不是因為你們太重了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.91,0:00:39.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 你們跟過來幹嘛啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.95,0:00:43.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要問為何 因為守護佳音是我的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.50,0:00:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？你說我胖？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.16,0:00:46.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.12,0:00:48.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你再說一遍！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.13,0:00:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.38,0:00:58.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.39,0:01:06.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麽又來這個！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.56,0:01:15.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深淵的祭壇…肯定就在附近了…哞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.96,0:02:53.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的腰啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.67,0:02:56.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喉嚨乾死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.55,0:02:57.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奧托！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.50,0:02:58.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.26,0:03:00.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.51,0:03:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 我是羅曼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.10,0:03:09.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 是維啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.64,0:03:12.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 總算通了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.77,0:03:14.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們現在在哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.48,0:03:17.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺這錢用得飛快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.61,0:03:20.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.40,0:03:23.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？換宗吾來接？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.46,0:03:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 我的水！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.57,0:03:25.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1484.571,1068.857)}喂喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.74,0:03:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1318.857,1066.571)}咦 掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.74,0:03:28.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,把我的水吐出來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.20,0:03:31.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這混球！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.50,0:03:33.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝款待哞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.62,0:03:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1453.715,1068.858)}-真好喝哞 喝爽了哞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.21,0:03:34.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟敢喝我的水！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.96,0:03:37.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳音 看那邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.96,0:03:41.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.01,0:03:41.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凉凉的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:44.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡竟然有泉水 這是何等的幸運啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.15,0:03:56.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.15,0:04:00.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:13.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他受了重傷 應該正躲在某處等待救援
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.33,0:04:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別讓他逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.17,0:04:21.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這邊 地上有血跡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.92,0:05:00.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒逃走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.97,0:05:14.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:16.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你一起的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.56,0:05:21.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許還能看到更多有趣的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.44,0:05:23.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「有趣」？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.69,0:05:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「不像樣」才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.86,0:05:30.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪邊都行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.87,0:05:33.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有你在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.13,0:05:41.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜蜂來電！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.34,0:05:43.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解析密碼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.21,0:05:45.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的能相信他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.67,0:05:47.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.93,0:05:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加斯這麼說的話 那就行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.51,0:05:53.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,方向修正 向西北方前進
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.56,0:05:54.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 太陽都要下山了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.49,0:06:15.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來今天就只能到這了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.79,0:06:20.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好勒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.00,0:06:24.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了各位 本大爺就展現下自己的手藝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:26.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.67,0:06:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 多麼醉人的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.01,0:06:37.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.06,0:06:40.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.56,0:06:42.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 也快讓我們嚐嚐…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.53,0:06:57.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是毒蘑菇啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.67,0:07:04.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本人第八軍特種部隊 修特·普萊斯中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.46,0:07:09.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望請教各位諮詢委員會成員的意見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.22,0:07:12.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得以發言 倍感光榮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.47,0:07:18.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下之前的發問不為其他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.56,0:07:21.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是關於加爾福．宗博伊爾執行長官
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.64,0:07:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對於行動代號「利瑪」的處理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.60,0:07:26.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應是由我等第八軍和行政機關
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.65,0:07:29.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,統一步調 齊心協力來共同面對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.73,0:07:34.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 近來宗博伊爾長官的獨斷專行令人難以保持沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.95,0:07:38.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知身為政府良心的各位又是做何考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.55,0:07:51.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能修好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.76,0:07:55.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 就差一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.93,0:07:57.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就又能跑起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.35,0:07:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.23,0:08:04.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡不著嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.69,0:08:06.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.33,0:08:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.95,0:08:21.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.29,0:08:25.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遇到了一堆可怕的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.87,0:08:27.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在也都是些不懂的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.71,0:08:32.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今後說不定也會發生些更不得了的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.30,0:08:36.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.43,0:08:38.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.14,0:08:42.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管發生什麼事 都有大家在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.56,0:08:47.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們會保護菲莉雅的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.57,0:08:51.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.65,0:08:52.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘑菇！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.78,0:08:55.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奧托！那是我的蘑菇！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.16,0:09:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.75,0:09:04.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.12,0:09:06.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定會一切順利的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.92,0:09:10.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 宗吾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.79,0:09:13.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信大家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.42,0:09:16.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…好了 修理完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.34,0:09:19.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天還得趕路 去睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.51,0:09:20.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.01,0:09:23.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有宗吾修好你真幸運 氣動車先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.07,0:09:38.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.07,0:09:41.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.74,0:09:43.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有隻發光的蝴蝶…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.38,0:09:52.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對象確認
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.46,0:09:54.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.26,0:09:56.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅 這邊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.72,0:09:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別想逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.06,0:10:14.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在小看我嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.20,0:10:25.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想死你了 混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.42,0:10:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅曼！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.38,0:10:33.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅曼 快起來！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.67,0:10:39.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還在那跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.60,0:10:47.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連抵抗的力氣都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.43,0:10:52.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老實點 這就幫你解脫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.98,0:10:59.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹…他媽的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.74,0:11:08.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.41,0:11:10.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.96,0:11:13.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你他媽的 竟然敢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.00,0:11:16.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕克 你去追利瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.92,0:11:17.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.05,0:11:20.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙可是我的獵物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.26,0:11:22.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不讓我幹掉他？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.93,0:11:23.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.64,0:11:32.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎唷…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.27,0:11:35.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也想去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.36,0:11:37.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.65,0:11:41.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就只能先把我打倒再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.41,0:11:53.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很瞭解你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.04,0:11:56.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞭解的不得了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.05,0:12:04.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來今晚有好夜景看了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.89,0:12:07.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑哪去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.76,0:12:11.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃到哪去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.69,0:12:19.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.77,0:12:20.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.94,0:12:22.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定會保護菲莉雅的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.99,0:12:27.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利瑪…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.08,0:12:31.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到你囉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.62,0:12:35.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.21,0:12:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.09,0:12:42.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑吧 快逃遠點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.84,0:12:46.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然會被射中的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.39,0:12:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要射了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.69,0:13:02.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休想再前進一步！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.36,0:13:10.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾 菲莉雅 快逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.58,0:13:12.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.33,0:13:12.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.08,0:13:14.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你小子！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.83,0:13:16.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.26,0:13:27.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 讓我感受一下你的拳頭吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.02,0:13:37.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅曼動力特別爆炸拳！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.94,0:13:40.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被躲過去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.44,0:13:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.62,0:13:57.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.18,0:14:16.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就知道你肯定會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.56,0:14:20.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你好久了 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.75,0:14:42.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你恨我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.88,0:14:44.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.38,0:14:46.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恨無力的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.01,0:14:51.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 那邊很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.01,0:14:52.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你懂的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.39,0:14:56.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以快來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.81,0:15:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來撲進我的懷裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.56,0:15:02.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,調皮的小貓咪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.32,0:15:07.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.68,0:15:37.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們搞什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.06,0:15:42.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿爾 有反應嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.81,0:15:47.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐…我的小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.73,0:15:49.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他媽的 沒用的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.15,0:15:51.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.32,0:15:59.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,諮詢委員會的諸位
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.54,0:16:02.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想在貝爾貝林療養所設宴款待您
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.62,0:16:08.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕是因為修特普萊斯中佐的報告
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.38,0:16:13.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,諸位長老的意見背後 是他們的謀慮和博學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.34,0:16:17.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我等一直對此深懷尊敬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.35,0:16:21.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在我等的宏願面前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.81,0:16:25.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種聰明有時或許也會成為障礙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.62,0:16:41.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真安靜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.54,0:16:44.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 畢竟平時都吵慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.92,0:16:49.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久沒有這麼寧靜的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.13,0:16:54.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.64,0:17:01.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡這種時光
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.48,0:17:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多蒙為什麽要開咖啡館？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.48,0:17:18.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前啊 隨手煮的咖啡被朋友誇獎了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.91,0:17:24.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身為軍人 我一直覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.87,0:17:30.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的這雙染滿血污的手 只會傷害别人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.09,0:17:32.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.80,0:17:35.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.09,0:17:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她對我說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.80,0:17:44.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「你的手上 有著能煮出美味咖啡的魔法」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.52,0:17:51.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她現在怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.32,0:17:54.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有個熟悉內部情況的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.49,0:17:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.49,0:18:03.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了隱藏秘密事項 她已經離開了人世
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.08,0:18:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 我不該問這些
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.41,0:18:08.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.42,0:18:10.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.71,0:18:14.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下定了決心 要保護好她的遺骨宗吾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.38,0:18:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.38,0:18:21.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 戲就演到這吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.09,0:18:22.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特務「蜜蜂」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.72,0:18:27.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能告訴我宗吾他們的去向嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.07,0:18:41.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.41,0:18:47.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.00,0:18:51.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳音 佳音！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.88,0:18:54.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.88,0:18:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.97,0:19:01.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.09,0:19:03.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.72,0:19:05.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.18,0:19:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫拉也不在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.48,0:19:10.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.27,0:19:12.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.15,0:19:14.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.28,0:19:30.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然有這種地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.91,0:19:31.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.34,0:19:38.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看那邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.68,0:19:44.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.90,0:19:53.71,injp,,0,0,0,,咲いていよう　これから少しのあいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.71,0:20:06.68,injp,,0,0,0,,君に出会い　花を揺らしてたんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.68,0:20:19.07,injp,,0,0,0,,伝えきれないことがたくさんあって
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.07,0:20:33.12,injp,,0,0,0,,この地に根を張り　春を待って息吹あげる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.12,0:20:49.39,injp,,0,0,0,,綿毛のようにただ　求めずに咲き誇ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.39,0:21:05.65,injp,,0,0,0,,それから僕らは大地をも覆うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.82,0:21:18.63,injp,,0,0,0,,見守ってくれた　あの人はいつでも…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.90,0:19:53.71,incn,,0,0,0,,只願在之後的這段時間裡 能保持綻放
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.71,0:20:06.68,incn,,0,0,0,,那時和你相遇  搖動著花瓣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.68,0:20:19.07,incn,,0,0,0,,有太多沒能全都告訴你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.07,0:20:33.12,incn,,0,0,0,,在這裡生根 等待春天 為它送上春之氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.39,0:21:05.65,incn,,0,0,0,,之後 我們會覆蓋大地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.82,0:21:18.63,incn,,0,0,0,,靜靜守護我們的那個人總是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.12,0:20:49.39,incn,,0,0,0,,就像蒲公英的絨毛 不求回報 傲然綻放
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.55,0:19:46.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.20,0:20:08.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.70,0:20:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.83,0:20:17.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.30,0:20:20.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.51,0:20:24.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.84,0:20:30.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道 但這裡很溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.18,0:20:33.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它來迎接我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.60,0:20:37.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.80,0:21:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.01,0:21:04.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.30,0:22:18.56,edjp,,0,0,0,,めざめに思うのは　あたらしい朝のなかで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.56,0:22:24.61,edjp,,0,0,0,,わたしはこの世界が好きなの　大好きなの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.61,0:22:29.78,edjp,,0,0,0,,ひかりに呼ばれたら　裸足のままでも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.78,0:22:32.91,edjp,,0,0,0,,向かいたくなる とめないで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.91,0:22:36.29,edjp,,0,0,0,,わたしもっともっと遠くへ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.29,0:22:41.38,edjp,,0,0,0,,ステップ踏みながらさがしてた それは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.38,0:22:50.80,edjp,,0,0,0,,きっとね 「冒険にでるよ」 こころが夢みてる扉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.80,0:22:54.76,edjp,,0,0,0,,今日が楽しくはじまる　レッツゴー！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.76,0:22:58.02,edjp,,0,0,0,,追いかけてみたあの雲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.02,0:23:00.52,edjp,,0,0,0,,どっちへ逃げたのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.52,0:23:03.81,edjp,,0,0,0,,はやくつかまえなくちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.81,0:23:06.94,edjp,,0,0,0,,楽しさはじけて　レッツゴー！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.94,0:23:10.20,edjp,,0,0,0,,追いかけてどこまでだって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.20,0:23:12.66,edjp,,0,0,0,,いっしょなら行けそう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.66,0:23:14.74,edjp,,0,0,0,,となりにいれば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.74,0:23:19.08,edjp,,0,0,0,,もうこわくないから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.30,0:22:18.56,edcn,,0,0,0,,在嶄新的清晨醒來 心中想的是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.56,0:22:24.61,edcn,,0,0,0,,我喜歡這個世界 最喜歡了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.61,0:22:29.78,edcn,,0,0,0,,被光呼喚著 就算是光著腳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.78,0:22:32.91,edcn,,0,0,0,,也想要前去 不要攔著我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.91,0:22:36.29,edcn,,0,0,0,,我要到更遠更遠的地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.29,0:22:41.38,edcn,,0,0,0,,踏著步伐找尋著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.38,0:22:50.80,edcn,,0,0,0,,那一定是 「去冒險吧」 我心中夢寐以求的門
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.80,0:22:54.76,edcn,,0,0,0,,今天開心地開始　Let's go！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.76,0:22:58.02,edcn,,0,0,0,,一直追著它看得雲朵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.02,0:23:00.52,edcn,,0,0,0,,跑到哪裡去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.52,0:23:03.81,edcn,,0,0,0,,要快點抓到它
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.81,0:23:06.94,edcn,,0,0,0,,快樂綻放　Let's go！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.94,0:23:10.20,edcn,,0,0,0,,追著它到天涯海角
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.20,0:23:12.66,edcn,,0,0,0,,和你一起就能到達
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.66,0:23:14.74,edcn,,0,0,0,,因為在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.74,0:23:19.08,edcn,,0,0,0,,就不再害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.78,0:23:29.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是那麼重要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.40,0:23:30.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是那麼喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.24,0:23:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.86,0:23:33.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.62,0:23:36.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集「彗星．路西法」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.70,0:23:37.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.99,0:23:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起來拿上通往冒險的車票哞！
